data.title: Secretary Kerry Meets With French Foreign Minister Fabius
data.meta_description: U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry meets with French Foreign Minister Laurent Fabius in his Outer Office at the U.S. Department of State in Washington, D.C., on April 19, 2015. [State Department photo/ Public Domain
